        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"William Kelley\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n William Kelley:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>What an amazing line up.</p>\n<p>Sounds like the Remoissenet was marked by 1992 botrytis.</p>\n<p>Andr\u00e9, as I\u2019m sure you know, was Pierre\u2019s son, and during his lifetime some of the Domaine\u2019s wines\u2014never, I think, all\u2014were released under his name. I think I\u2019ve seen the '78 with the Domaine label too.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>William,</p>\n<p>I think you\u2019re likely correct on the 92 and botrytis.</p>\n<p>Interesting, but perhaps unsurprising (being Burgundy) that the labels were varied. Thanks!</p>",
